'''維基競賽'''（英語：Wikiracing）是一個運用[[網路百科全書|網路百科全書]]—[[維基百科|維基百科]]進行的競賽遊戲，玩家依靠點擊維基百科的[[超連結|內部連結]]從給定的起點條目移動到終點。<ref>Aubrey Whelan. [https://www.inquirer.com/philly/living/20100721__Wikiracing__picking_up_speed_among_college_students.html "'Wikiracing' picking up speed among college students".] {{Wayback|url=https://www.inquirer.com/philly/living/20100721__Wikiracing__picking_up_speed_among_college_students.html |date=20191220185818 }} ''[[The_Philadelphia_Inquirer|The Philadelphia Inquirer]]'', 7/21/2010.</ref><ref>Ben Jones. [https://www.post-gazette.com/business/tech-news/2010/07/11/Latest-game-for-bored-students-Wikiracing/stories/201007110177 "Latest game for bored students? Wikiracing".] {{Wayback|url=https://www.post-gazette.com/business/tech-news/2010/07/11/Latest-game-for-bored-students-Wikiracing/stories/201007110177 |date=20191220185815 }} ''[[Star_Tribune|Star Tribune]]'', 6/20/2010.</ref><ref>Ariel Doctoroff. [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/07/22/want-to-waste-an-hour-or_n_654619.html "Want To Waste An Hour (Or Three)? Go On A Wikirace".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/07/22/want-to-waste-an-hour-or_n_654619.html |date=20170803120548 }} ''[[Huffington_Post|Huffington Post]]'', 7/22/10.</ref><ref>Colin Hepke (2008). [http://spider.eecs.umich.edu/tbp/Newsletters/F08/F08Second_Actives.pdf "On Your Mark, Get Set, Wikipedia"!] {{Wayback|url=http://spider.eecs.umich.edu/tbp/Newsletters/F08/F08Second_Actives.pdf |date=20120403222940 }} Cornerstone 2(3), 8.</ref><ref>Ben Jones. [http://www.ecollegetimes.com/music/students-glued-to-computers-turn-wikipedia-into-a-game-1.2494012#.TsNA68NFuso "Students glued to computers turn Wikipedia into a game".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ecollegetimes.com/music/students-glued-to-computers-turn-wikipedia-into-a-game-1.2494012#.TsNA68NFuso |date=20120718211900 }} ''[[College_Times|College Times]]'', 7/8/2010.</ref>此外也有著能夠進行維基競賽的外部網站。<ref>John Walker. [http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2010/06/10/searching-for-fun-wikipedia-game/ "Searching For Fun: Wikipedia Game".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2010/06/10/searching-for-fun-wikipedia-game/ |date=20200718164420 }} ''[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]'', 6/10/2010.</ref>

在[[英語維基百科|英語維基百科]]中，「[[英國|英國]]」和任意一個條目的中間平均間隔著3.67個連結。一些特殊規則的維基競賽也會禁止使用「[[美國|美國]]」這一連結，以增加遊戲難度。<ref>Brock Read. [http://chronicle.com/blogs/wiredcampus/6-degrees-of-wikipedia/3973 "6 Degrees of Wikipedia".] {{Wayback|url=http://chronicle.com/blogs/wiredcampus/6-degrees-of-wikipedia/3973 |date=20120118231853 }} ''[[The_Chronicle_of_Higher_Education|The Chronicle of Higher Education]]'', 5/28/2008.</ref>

2019年7月，出現了一個叫做「The Wiki Game」的維基競賽網站，讓用戶可以在線上與其他的玩家一起競賽，爭奪分數和排行榜名次。而後該網站又受到了網路紅人{{link-en|Game Grumps}}的實況遊玩，使得維基競賽得到了許多的知名度。「The Wiki Game」同時也有著手機應用版，開放在[[App_Store|App Store]]下載。

